POE-Component-Lightspeed version 0.03
=====================================

This is the romping grounds of IKC2

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

	POE
	Graph
	Carp
	Time::HiRes
	Socket

